      "default_ttl": null,
      "description": "Counter - a widget designed to display the number of objects that match a certain filter condition. In it, instead of a specific data source or sources, a condition is set for which all objects that the Pixel Board application has access to and that are created based on the selected data schema will be checked for compliance. Filtering is applied to objects of the same type, because they must have the same fields. The result of the widget that it displays is the number of objects that match the condition. The Counter widget has the ability to issue alarms: it can be configured from one to three conditions for switching to an alarm.",
